{"tid":1453801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗污名化！！！不要叫速龍！試著叫蛆蟲！不要叫popo或狗咁可愛！試著叫屎蟲","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:22:32.000Z","uid":190127,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"574b9d76d462a6fdf46ad781361f74963e648f52","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"我地絕對唔可以習慣俾班渣蟲叫小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先大家睇下呢篇關於盧旺達大屠殺：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/465292153502788/posts/2524969274201722?s=644935872&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F465292153502788%2Fposts%2F2524969274201722%3Fs%3D644935872%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=309789d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/465292153502788/posts/2524969274201722?s=644935872&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺一個人，縱有仇怨，還是很難下手，但殺一隻曱甴，很容易。1994年4月，非洲中部這個千丘之國血流成河，一百天屠殺了100萬人，胡圖族的軍隊、民兵，以致平民手起刀落，見圖西族人就斬殺，因為被殺的，不是一個個有名有姓有職業活生生的人，而是被貶為曱甴的一個群體。<br />\n<br />\n要軍隊、民兵、平民打得重手，殺得下手，就先把要對付的對象不當人。<br />\n<br />\n納粹對付猶太人都係用呢招<br />\n<br />\n污名化呢樣野係可以好恐怖 所以我地都要反洗腦<br />\n[size=5][red]要不斷重申示威者唔係小強 <br />\n<br />\n同埋要以彼之道 還施彼身<br />\n叫佢地蛆蟲！屎蟲！</span></span>"},{"pid":"61933ffbb957b856a258e01156a6f13b826573ff","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b64bdc8b2dcd54eac030a60a764b991bbbd49f1a","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4140326bf63a483413a03b36a5c07d9b28417c","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee65b1caea6823dcb0a4560e4f2223428ffe92d","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"蛆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65365eb0f1d741b6f28ca0d03c4bf19668ce997a","tid":1453801,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"有d繞口"},{"pid":"89a64c57cf724c9b7f5765761f85e6ae0bb472bc","tid":1453801,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"叫返佢地甲由"},{"pid":"0a209d463d9b8766dc0167e39882a6c9a855d834","tid":1453801,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"屎蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287e75cbe26b3362ac9a342c8db2507f62c46214","tid":1453801,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4688e3be3e3bd5399a5910880641d8b24e522214","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6a3c514b0078c6c5337a928d8fbfe3fd8408886","tid":1453801,"uid":190127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:45:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82846bdec47731aa81ff4291d4338a4173a0c70a","tid":1453801,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a64c57cf724c9b7f5765761f85e6ae0bb472bc","tid":1453801,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"叫返佢地甲由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:05:41.000Z","msg":"&quot;僑裝&quot;警員為「曱甴